description: Retrieves information about the specified association between a service network and a resource configuration.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the association.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The date and time that the association was created, in ISO-8601 format.

nested_items.name: createdBy
nested_items.description: The account that created the association.

nested_items.name: domainName
nested_items.description: The domain name of the service.

nested_items.name: hostedZoneId
nested_items.description: The ID of the hosted zone.

nested_items.name: failureCode
nested_items.description: The failure code.

nested_items.name: failureReason
nested_items.description: The reason the association request failed.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The ID of the association.

nested_items.name: isManagedAssociation
nested_items.description: Indicates whether the association is managed by Amazon.

nested_items.name: lastUpdatedAt
nested_items.description: The most recent date and time that the association was updated, in ISO-8601 format.

nested_items.name: privateDnsEntry
nested_items.description: The private DNS entry for the service.

nested_items.name: domainName
nested_items.description: The domain name of the service.

nested_items.name: hostedZoneId
nested_items.description: The ID of the hosted zone.

nested_items.name: resourceConfigurationArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the association.

nested_items.name: resourceConfigurationId
nested_items.description: The ID of the resource configuration that is associated with the service network.

nested_items.name: resourceConfigurationName
nested_items.description: The name of the resource configuration that is associated with the service network.

nested_items.name: serviceNetworkArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the service network that is associated with the resource configuration.

nested_items.name: serviceNetworkId
nested_items.description: The ID of the service network that is associated with the resource configuration.

nested_items.name: serviceNetworkName
nested_items.description: The name of the service network that is associated with the resource configuration.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of the association.
